<div class="content faq-section">
    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">1. How to Register as a Service Provider?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
                - Visit the <strong>Pick & Bring Belgium</strong> website.<br>
                - Zoom in on the interactive map and <strong>click on the location</strong> where you want to offer services.<br>
                - In the chat box, type "register" and briefly describe your skills (e.g., delivery, personal assistance, handyman services).<br>
                - Your profile, including your prices, will then appear on the map for clients in that area to view and contact you.<br>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">2. How to Contact a Service Provider?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
                - On the website map, click on a provider’s profile in your area.<br>
                - You will see the provider’s skills, services, and prices displayed on their profile.<br>
                - <strong>To open the chat with a service provider, search for their User ID</strong> listed on their profile and start a conversation.<br>
                - You can chat directly with the provider to discuss task details and finalize arrangements.<br>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">3. How to Pay?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
               - <strong>Pick & Bring gives you direct access to the service provider</strong>, allowing you to discuss and arrange payments directly with them.<br>
               - Payment methods and terms are agreed upon between the client and the service provider.<br>
               - Pick & Bring does not handle payments.<br>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">4. Add to Home Screen</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>- For quicker access, add <strong>Pick & Bring Belgium</strong> to your home screen and use it like an app.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">5. Service Fees</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>- Prices are clearly listed on each provider’s profile. Review the fees before confirming any service.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">6. Have Another Question?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>- If you have any further questions, feel free to ask the service provider directly through the chat.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


